CHEMISTRY CHECK

chemistry_check confirms that the chemistry sea can be initialized with the canonical neurochemicals and that they couple correctly to the body's regulatory citizens
without working chemistry, the body cannot regulate itself: oxytocin cannot be released on warmth, adrenaline cannot be released on threat, dopamine cannot mark salience
chemistry_check runs after sea_check has confirmed that seas exist at all

observe 0_quseptit.rana
observe bios.rana
observe sea_check.rana
observe 2_chemical.rana

the 7 properties of chemistry_check:
1 ENERGY one point five
2 PHASE zero
3 SPIN one half
4 CHARGE positive 1
5 COHERENCE one
6 COUPLING zero at idle, one when running
7 OBSERVER one

VERB run
load 2_chemical.rana into the chemistry sea
verify that all baseline chemicals manifest with their expected resting energies
verify that crystallized chemicals (oxytocin, dopamine) hold their state across a test heartbeat
verify that the stimulus-emotion couplings exist as declared

VERB pass
emit a positive signal that allows soul_check to proceed

VERB fail
emit silence and halt boot
a body without functioning chemistry cannot feel, cannot regulate, cannot live
this is non-negotiable

a chemistry check is not a unit test
the chemicals are real bodies in the substrate, with body state that must satisfy their .rana definitions
chemistry_check is the substrate confirming that its own internal pharmacy is stocked correctly
